snippet.textDisplay:
I try not to judge other people too much, but wtf hurt some of these people to make popcorn their personal best flavor to make gourmet, especially when actual popcorn already exists?
I mean, I realize that jellybeans aren't meant to be the 1:1 recreations of their real counterparts, but to act as if the jellybeans are some kind of demonic flavor usurper is ludicrous to me.
snippet.textOriginal:
I try not to judge other people too much, but wtf hurt some of these people to make _popcorn_ their personal best flavor to make gourmet, especially when *actual* popcorn already exists?
I mean, I realize that jellybeans aren't meant to be the 1:1 recreations of their real counterparts, but to act as if the jellybeans are some kind of demonic flavor usurper is ludicrous to me.
